title: Miley Cyrus Carries a Cup of Unicorn Tears in New York City
text: Miley Cyrus holds onto colorful bags that match her loud outfit while taking photos with fans out and about on Wednesday night (September 30) in New York City . The 22-year-old entertainer also had a cup labeled “Unicorn Tears” attached to her hip! Meanwhile, Miley is in town getting ready for the season premiere of Saturday [...] »
